You want to tell me when you
plan on letting us out of here

41:02.111 --> 41:04.810
for good? Michigan penal code,
article 328:

41:04.853 --> 41:06.855
a person who commits
unlawful imprisonment

41:06.899 --> 41:09.728
is guilty of a felony.

41:09.771 --> 41:11.556
What?

